<h1 class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
  Data Deletion Instructions
</h1>
<p class="mb-6 text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
  If you wish to delete your data from TangoCloud, please follow these steps:
</p>
<ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-4 text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
  <li>
    Send a POST request to our data deletion endpoint:
    <code class="block bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-100 p-2 rounded-md mt-2">
      https://tangocloud.app/auth/facebook/data-deletion/
    </code>
  </li>
  <li>
    Include your Facebook user ID in the request.
  </li>
</ol>
<p class="text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
  Your data will be deleted from our system within 30 days of the request.
</p>
